262
00:10:44,770 --> 00:10:47,231
Prima da Fiona e do Declan.

263
00:10:47,314 --> 00:10:48,690
A garota da metanfetamina?

264
00:10:48,774 --> 00:10:50,150
Sim,
mas ela está limpa agora.

265
00:10:50,234 --> 00:10:51,652
