há dois meses.

266
00:10:51,735 --> 00:10:52,694
Legal.

267
00:10:53,820 --> 00:10:54,905
Ei, desculpe, cara,
estamos fechados.

268
00:10:54,988 --> 00:10:56,240
Volte para...

269
00:10:56,323 --> 00:10:58,492
Eu sou da Força-Tarefa
Metropolitana de Drogas.

270
00:10:58,575 --> 00:10:59,535
