287
00:11:39,074 --> 00:11:40,117
Sim, senhor!

288
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,243
Pete?!

289
00:11:41,326 --> 00:11:43,036
Sim, eu entendi.

290
00:11:48,166 --> 00:11:49,668
