de compartilhar com a turma?

306
00:12:27,247 --> 00:12:29,208
Uh, na verdade, sim,
há.

307
00:12:29,291 --> 00:12:31,376
Esta noite Fritz Helder
and the Phantoms

308
00:12:31,460 --> 00:12:33,170
