404
00:16:33,327 --> 00:16:46,632
♪♪♪♪♪

405
00:16:46,715 --> 00:16:49,134
Hum, eu acabei de ver
a Victoria no banheiro.

406
00:16:49,218 --> 00:16:50,260
Usando drogas.

407
00:16:50,344 --> 00:16:52,763
